Spotlight


"The people, the culture and the passion at Syros makes me feel like we can achieve big things." - Nisha, Senior Scientist 

"One of the things that makes Syros a great place to work is how approachable everyone is, including the management team. I really appreciate people's openness to discuss new ideas or concerns either in formal settings or while grabbing a cup of coffee." - Kristin, Senior Research Associate 

"I'm excited about the promise of our medicines. I'm excited to be so intimately involved in the drug development process. I'm excited to see the growth and the development of the company and my colleagues. I'm excited about all the learning I get to do every day when I come to work." - Alex, Associate Director, Regulatory Affairs 






