syros pharmaceuticals inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Biotech & Pharma
Sub-Industry: Specialty Pharma
Syros Pharmaceuticals, Inc. operates as a biopharmaceutical company. The Company focuses on developing treatments for cancer and immune-mediated diseases, as well as building a pipeline of gene control medicines. Syros Pharmaceuticals conducts business worldwide.




